HEADWORD: hospitalisation insurance
<hw>hospitalisation insurance</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A form of
<isa>medical insurance</isa> that pays for all or part of the fees for a
person's residence and treatment in a hospital.</def>⟦br⟧
